data.description: This is a BEAUTIFULLY upgraded home that has been recently refreshed and completely move-in ready! It's also energy efficient with solar panels installed in 2022 and a very low HOA in a highly desirable community of Country Roads within Murrieta. This home boasts a 3 car garage, 5 spacious bedrooms with one downstairs, 3 full bathrooms and so many new upgrades for the next owner. The entire interior of the home has been freshly painted, the exterior fascia has been painted, new Berber carpet in the bedrooms and living areas otherwise there is laminate flooring downstairs in the formal dining room and main floor hallway as well as tile flooring. The kitchen is gorgeous with new quartz countertops, backsplash, beautifully painted cabinets, and LED recessed lighting. All guest bedrooms in this home are very spacious and the primary bedroom is huge with a wall of windows bringing in natural light but also blinds for privacy. The primary bathroom has separate vanities, a walk-in closet and a separate soaking tub alongside the shower and the upstairs guest bathroom has dual sinks with a separate shower. The laundry room is conveniently located upstairs and it has a utility sink and built-in cabinets for plenty of storage. The backyard is finished nicely and is basically maintenance-free with a clean concrete patio, DG gravel, fence liner and concrete down both side-yards. Don't miss out on this move-in ready beautiful home!
